        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: pharmacological inhibition of mGlur7 results in changes in spontaneous miniature synaptic events, which strongly implies a presynaptic regulation.. Experimental description: Cell culture\nPrimary cultures of cerebellar cells were prepared from mGlu4 knock-out mice (Pekhletski et al., 1996), as previously described (Van Vliet et al., 1989)." ;
